snippet.title: Transcending Vibrations
snippet.description: 100% original meditation music for higher consciousness by artist/producer Brian Woodcock of Massachusetts. Transcending Vibrations, Pinealwave, and Dubwave are the three different artist names under the label of Woodcock Productions, bringing three unique styles of powerful, consciousness expanding meditation music.
